(pr gurmuK qy mnmuK-ieh) swrI bxqr prmwqmw ny Awp hI bxweI hY[
(sB jIvW ivc ivAwpk ho ky) auh Awp hI sB kuJ krdw hY qy (jIvW pwsoN) krWdw hY, auh Awp hI jgq dI swrI Kyf clw irhw hY[
hy nwnk! auh Awp hI Awpxy ie`k srUp qoN byAMq rUpW rMgW vwlw bixAw hoieAw hY[ (ieh swrw bhu rMgI jgq) aus ie`k ivc hI lIn ho jWdw hY ]9]2]36]
