(jdoN mnu`K nUM ieh inscw hovy ik) sB suKW dw mwlk hrI (myrw rwKw hY) qW auh bhuq sOKw jIvn ibqIq krdw hY[
hy pRBU! ijs nUM ieh inscw hY ik qUM ijMd dw pRwxW dw mn dw suK dwqw hYN, qy jo kuJ qUM krdw hYN auhI huMdw hY, auh mnu`K Awqmk AwnMd mwxdw hY ]1]
